title: Watch: VARSITY Barely Survives Dancing “U R My Only One” At Double Speed
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
Rookie group VARSITY has jumped on the double speed dance trend for hilarious — and unsuccessful — results. 
The group tackled their song “U R My Only One,” and with the choreography taxing even at normal speed, the group ended up adding tumbles, collisions, and general struggles to the sped-up version. 
VARSITY just debuted on January 5, and is comprised of seven Korean members and five Chinese members. 
Check out their dance practice below at double speed as well as normal speed.
